body.p:
A document type (configuration) can be loaded from the following locations:

internal preferences - The document type configuration is stored in the application's
            Internal preferences;

additional frameworks directories - The document type configuration is loaded from one
          of the specified Additional frameworks directories list;

add-ons - An add-on can contribute a framework. You can manage the add-ons locations in
          the Add-ons preferences
            page;

the frameworks folder - The main folder containing framework
          configurations.
